{
  "_doc": "Full COGS (product + shipping) per order for the BeProfit dashboard. method self|d2d (from Shopify shippingLine). qty = units of that product in the order. Cost types: full_usd (x rate) / full_ils (direct ILS) by method+qty / comfy split (product_per_unit_usd + shipping_usd) / product_per_unit_usd + ship_ils_flat. qty above a tier's max reuses the top tier; a missing method falls back to d2d. Source: Nicole supplier tables + economics.md. Order matters: first matching product wins.",
